                    <h2>Philosophy</h2>
                    <img src="~/images/coopSoccer.png" class="rounded float-sm-right">
                    Our philosophy is to develop good and positive rapport with the participants and to make certain their journey with the league is unforgettable. 
                    Transparency and respect to all will be the core to its operation. We are committed to the recreation and maintenance of a peaceful and secured atmosphere. 
                    We are dedicated to address unforeseen circumstances/issues in a manner responsible and balance decision making. We embrace diversity and value the integrity
                     of all with no distinction. Through the program, participants will recognize the importance to self-engage in sport regiment to stay healthy.
